  "body": "I noticed that when I use hardhat to call `eth_sendTransaction`, such as `contract.deploy`, if it is sent to a node that supports eip 1559(local hardhat node or goerli) , it will call `eth_feeHistory`, but it returns undefined.\r\n\r\nThe corresponding code logic is in  `_suggestEip1559FeePriceValues()` of `gas-providers.ts`\r\n",
